{"tid":727871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「代提款60萬元　可獲5.5萬報酬」　 fb撳錢騙局　呃按金千元","createTime":"2018-07-03T10:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-15T19:32:19.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a99798947b0d00f478676a846f5e75bd4a2326ae","tid":727871,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T10:43:19.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180703/20438435\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180703%2F20438435&d=%2B3YnwNggwi91A7jPWPPQmnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=c5188225\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180703%2F20438435&h=7fb05dd0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180703/20438435</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月03日 <br />\n<br />\n「代提款60萬元　可獲5.5萬報酬」　<br />\nfb撳錢騙局　呃按金千元<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180703/large/a1001b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180703%2Flarge%2Fa1001b.gif&h=16e34095&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■事主最初按facebook的撳機提款招聘帖子應徵，最終被騙財。受訪者提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】暑假臨近，不少學生哥、待業人士四出尋找兼職工作，賺取外快，但不少騙徒覷準機會，在熱門網上平台發招聘帖文，強調短時間內可「搵快錢」。《蘋果》找到受騙事主自白，踢爆新興的「假撳錢黨」騙局，聲稱代為撳機提款，撳60萬元便可獲5.5萬元報酬，過程僅需兩至三小時，但要求先交500元按金。有事主更連續被哄騙兩次失款共1,000元，事後大嘆：「可能我入世未深，有冇咁大隻蛤乸隨街跳呀？搵快錢有冇可能呀？」<br />\n<br />\n記者：李啟發　劉卓瑩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現年20歲的劉先生數月前在facebook見到招聘帖文，表明「零風險快錢限期最後2日」，遂透過whatsapp聯絡「僱主」Kelvin。對方透過錄音表明工作僅純粹幫朋友撳錢，「撳走30張（信用）卡（嘅錢），每張撳2萬，30張總共60萬，就有5.5萬（收入）」；另可選擇撳15張信用卡（30萬元），報酬2.8萬元。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180703/large/a1001a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180703%2Flarge%2Fa1001a.gif&h=986c4776&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■「僱主」Kelvin在whatsapp向求職者要求先支付500至800元按金，或提供住址證明。<br />\n稱「唔會犯法」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nKelvin強調過程最長僅兩小時，並會安排專車接送往油尖旺一帶撳錢，完事後即場以現金出糧，但要求必須先交500元按金。劉先生決定先試做15張信用卡，並過數500元給對方。不過，Kelvin其後以「老細唔畀佢攞咁少卡」為由，要求劉加碼至撳30張卡。劉氣憤稱：「交咗錢之後，佢（騙徒）又話唔得喎，作咗好多個理由，我已經開始覺得受騙，（但）我畀多次機會佢，加多500蚊畀佢。」劉前後共付1,000元，但對方即去如黃鶴失去聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n記者放蛇聯絡Kelvin，他聲稱「做埋呢一、兩日就唔做」，又強調過程「同普普通通撳錢一樣，完全唔會犯法，完全冇風險」，並指曾有人撳錢後走佬，令他及公司損失60萬，故要求先付按金，「我哋唔係驚你走數，淨係要confirm到你出嚟」。但當記者問及「撳咁多錢，真係唔犯法？」他突然發惡稱：「你呢個卧底，你同我行X開啦，你呢個差佬烏龜卧底。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n求職騙案趨增<br />\n<br />\n網上求職騙案有上升趨勢，根據警方統計，今年首季接獲58宗個案，涉款780萬元，金額超越去年及前年全年數字；相反，去年及前年全年分別只有87及51宗同類騙案，損失金額分別為670萬及700萬元。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n折磨<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n【暑期求職陷阱】「撳錢黨」走資洗黑錢　幫手撳都犯法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【暑期求職陷阱】「撳錢黨」走資洗黑錢　幫手撳都犯法<br />\n<br />\n兼職打字員淪違法淘寶打手"},{"pid":"2c22a17e3aa335a99956fe886d86b80b8c80d391","tid":727871,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T10:44:41.000Z","msg":"廿歲中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb0792f7f54ada33df8e7fceb9f67faa8dbefd0a","tid":727871,"uid":98386,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T10:47:40.000Z","msg":"唔知死差佬會唔會主動去查呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312ed73a8df154377315032d1a757a4955cf13fe","tid":727871,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:15:06.000Z","msg":"究竟幾on 9先信<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce838152c3b3c32cfc3461543352bf82873619ed","tid":727871,"uid":62167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:17:10.000Z","msg":"仲話香港人智力高<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40725c4eb43aec822a289b63fa8291018b4c8e59","tid":727871,"uid":154224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:49:03.000Z","msg":"點解問犯唔犯法可以知道佢係放蛇咁醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c298f0055e99a459fe51ade33bc109e078603dea","tid":727871,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2c22a17e3aa335a99956fe886d86b80b8c80d391","tid":727871,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T10:44:41.000Z","msg":"廿歲中招<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T11:54:24.000Z","msg":"仲要俾兩次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27c45b81572883c8b717482c66fcba5b2608af9e","tid":727871,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:05:59.000Z","msg":"Haha<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 做老千做到咁撚cheap 雞 真係衰過阿受害人<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n搞呢搞路 得果一千蚊 仲驚畀人拉嘅<br />\n<br />\n不如去做侍仔 等人打賞一百幾十仲冇咁煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd4255f0337195ffe74f2533e48d9211cc7c1203","tid":727871,"uid":37661,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:18:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「交咗錢之後，佢（騙徒）又話唔得喎，作咗好多個理由，我已經開始覺得受騙，（但）我畀多次機會佢，加多500蚊畀佢。」</span><br />\n<br />\n畀多次機會佢呃。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9946322312abc6861b8d3afd65ab014837b3b18e","tid":727871,"uid":179967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:19:34.000Z","msg":"過數有銀行number kelvin會走得甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"899523da766b4823d5ba72cfdc1e8397033813ec","tid":727871,"uid":57787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-03T12:21:44.000Z","msg":"過數應該好易查？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e840514055da83269570